Aloha President Kouchi, Speaker Nakamura, and Members of the Legislature:
This is to inform you that on June 5, 2026, the following bill was signed into law:
S.B. NO. 2756, H.D. 1, C.D. 1 RELATING TO CONSERVATION ENFORCEMENT.
