S.B. NO.
"^1
1 SECTION 2. There is appropriated out of the general
2 revenues of the State of Hawaii the sum of $2,365,000 or so much
3 thereof as may be necessary for fiscal year 2026-2027 for
4 equipment for the Hawaii island branch of the division of
5 conservation and resources enforcement of the department of land
6 and natural resources, to be allocated as follows:
7 (1) $365,000 for one maritime enforcement patrol vessel,
8 complete with audible and visual emergency equipment;
9 and
10 (2) $2,000,000 for twenty police-marked patrol vehicles,
11 complete with audible and visual emergency equipment.
12 The sum appropriated shall be expended by the department of
13 land and natural resources for the purposes of this Act.
14 SECTION 3. This Act shall take effect on July 1, 2026.
